<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Notificações</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-B4gt1jrGC7Jh4AgTPSdUtOBvfO8sh+WyUEHsmsLlqLs2tnGdC5l/rh2v9tJZhZ9w" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <!-- Adicione outros estilos conforme necessário -->
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .notification-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 50px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            position: relative; /* Adiciona posição relativa para o posicionamento absoluto do laço */
        }

        .notification-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .notification-image {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            border: 3px solid #fff;
        }

            .notification-image img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                object-fit: cover;
            }

        .notification-ribbon {
            position: absolute;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            background-image: url('https://i.imgur.com/w0PXAdz.png');
            background-size: cover;
            bottom: -5px;
            right: -5px;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .notification-item .notification-text {
            flex: 1;
        }

        /* Adiciona a classe para a imagem no canto inferior direito */
        .corner-image {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            background-image: url('caminho-da-sua-imagem.png'); /* Substitua pelo caminho da sua imagem */
            background-size: cover;
            border-radius: 0; /* Remove a borda circular */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="notification-container">
        <a href="@Url.Action("Details", "Memorial", new { id = 1 })" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
        <div class="notification-item">
            <div class="notification-image">
                <img src="https://dotnethow.net/images/actors/actor-5.jpeg" alt="Foto 1" />
            </div>
            <div class="notification-image">
                <img src="https://dotnethow.net/images/actors/actor-3.jpeg" alt="Foto 2" />
                <div class="notification-ribbon"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="notification-text">
                <p>Will começou a seguir o memorial de Aly</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="notification-container" >
        <a href="@Url.Action("Details", "Memorial", new { id = 2 })" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
        <div class="notification-item">
            <div class="notification-image">
                <img src="https://dotnethow.net/images/actors/actor-1.jpeg" alt="Foto 1" />
                <div class="notification-ribbon"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="notification-text">
                <p>Hoje faz 1 ano desde que Matty nos deixou, relembre algumas memorias acessando o memorial dele.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <!-- Adicione outros scripts conforme necessário -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-b12n3kVUdFjmO6IPYl8v2wWqQZ8yVHW6HO4Bsce8xj1jgrvqwe1DB5M/1OQm8fGt" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-B4gt1jrGC7Jh4AgTPSdUtOBvfO8sh+WyUEHsmsLlqLs2tnGdC5l/rh2v9tJZhZ9w" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
